/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 215.10 Tm
(normal.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 194.60 Tm
(The close should not feel like a sudden ambush. It should feel like the natural end of a well-framed) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 181.20 Tm
(process.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 160.80 Tm
("If the house qualifies, the numbers are lower, and the concerns are clear, would moving forward make) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 147.80 Tm
(sense?") Tj
