/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 711.60 Tm
("These questions help the system determine what your home may qualify for.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 685.60 Tm
(5. The Status Quo Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 665.10 Tm
(Purpose: reveal that doing nothing has a cost. This is the most important economic frame in solar.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 644.70 Tm
("Keeping things the same means continuing with the utility bill as it is, including future changes.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 618.70 Tm
(6. The Comparison Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 598.20 Tm
(Purpose: stop isolated price judgment. Every price is judged against something.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 577.80 Tm
("Let us compare monthly to monthly, predictability to predictability, and long-term value to long-) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 564.80 Tm
(term value.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 538.80 Tm
(7. The Ownership Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 518.30 Tm
(Purpose: connect solar to an idea homeowners already value.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 497.90 Tm
("You chose ownership with the house. This is about seeing whether more control over energy also makes) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 484.90 Tm
(sense.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 458.90 Tm
(8. The Qualification Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 438.40 Tm
(Purpose: create honest scarcity without fake urgency. Not every house, roof, credit profile, or) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 425.00 Tm
(usage pattern qualifies.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 404.60 Tm
("The first question is not whether you buy. The first question is whether the home qualifies.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 378.60 Tm
(9. The Transparency Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 358.10 Tm
(Purpose: build trust by naming the parts people usually fear: cost, contract, credit, roof,) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 344.70 Tm
(timeline, and cancellation terms.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 324.30 Tm
("I am going to explain the good parts and the important details so there are no surprises.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 298.30 Tm
(10. The Objection Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 277.80 Tm
(Purpose: make objections collaborative.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 257.40 Tm
("Concerns are not a problem. They are how we make sure the decision is clean.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 231.40 Tm
(11. The Decision Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 210.90 Tm
(Purpose: prevent endless thinking after clarity is reached.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 190.50 Tm
("If the concerns are handled and the numbers are better, then the decision is really whether you want) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 177.50 Tm
(the better option or the current one.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 151.50 Tm
(12. The Comfort Frame) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 131.00 Tm
(Purpose: protect the homeowner and the deal after the close. A rushed signature can become a) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 117.60 Tm
(cancellation. Comfort creates durability.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 97.20 Tm
("Before you sign, tell me what this means in your own words so I know I explained it clearly.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 282.00 30.00 Tm
(Page 6 of 16) Tj
