(Objection: "I do not trust solar.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 705.50 Tm
(This is not a product objection. It is a trust and evidence objection. Reframe from belief to) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 692.10 Tm
(verification.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 671.70 Tm
("Fair. You should not trust a concept blindly. Let us verify the parts that matter: production) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 658.70 Tm
(estimate, warranty, payment, utility process, roof impact, and what happens if the numbers do not) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 645.70 Tm
(work.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 619.70 Tm
(Objection: "Is this free?") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 599.20 Tm
(Be extremely careful. Do not call financed solar free. Reframe free to upfront cost, if accurate.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 578.80 Tm
("Not free. The accurate way to say it is that there may be no upfront out-of-pocket cost if you) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 565.80 Tm
(qualify. You would still have a payment or program terms, and we compare that against your current) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 552.80 Tm
(utility bill.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 526.80 Tm
(Objection: "It sounds too good to be true.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 506.30 Tm
(This is a trust signal. Slow down and reframe around details.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 485.90 Tm
("That is a healthy reaction. Let us go through the exact numbers and terms. If anything does not make) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 472.90 Tm
(sense, we should stop.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 446.90 Tm
(Objection: "What if I move?") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 426.40 Tm
(Reframe from fear to exit options, but do not overpromise. Explain the actual transfer, payoff, or) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 413.00 Tm
(assumption options based on the agreement.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 392.60 Tm
("Good question. The answer depends on the financing and contract terms. Let us look at the exact) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 379.60 Tm
(options: transfer, payoff, or how it is handled during sale. I do not want to guess on that.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 353.60 Tm
(Objection: "What about my roof?") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 333.10 Tm
(Roof concerns are valid. Reframe solar as dependent on roof suitability, not blind installation.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 312.70 Tm
("The roof has to make sense first. That is why the site survey and engineering review matter. If the) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 299.70 Tm
(roof is not a fit, we address that before moving forward.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 273.70 Tm
(Objection: "What if the panels do not produce enough?") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 253.20 Tm
(Reframe to design, production estimate, monitoring, warranty, and utility rules.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 232.80 Tm
("That is exactly why the production estimate matters. We look at usage, roof angle, shading, system) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 219.80 Tm
(size, and the warranty or performance terms so you know what is being projected.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 193.80 Tm
(Objection: "I heard solar is a scam.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 173.30 Tm
(Do not argue with rumors. Reframe from industry reputation to company process and transparent) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 159.90 Tm
(documentation.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 139.50 Tm
("There are definitely bad actors in every industry. That is why we slow down, show the documents,) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 126.50 Tm
(explain the numbers, and make sure you know who is responsible for each step.") Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 100.50 Tm
(Objection: "I do not want a credit check.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 80.00 Tm
(Reframe as permission-based qualification. Do not run anything without clear authorization.) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
