/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 630.10 Tm
(- "Compare" instead of "convince") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 613.70 Tm
(- "Qualify" instead of "buy") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 597.30 Tm
(- "Next step" instead of "sign up") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 580.90 Tm
(- "More predictable" instead of "guaranteed" unless the agreement truly guarantees it) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 564.50 Tm
(- "No upfront out-of-pocket cost" instead of "free" when accurate) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 548.10 Tm
(- "Based on today's numbers" instead of overpromising future savings) Tj
/F2 11.5 Tf
