/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 224.90 Tm
("Third, we compare both options side by side. If solar is not clearly better, we do not force it.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 204.90 Tm
(This frame is powerful because it makes you look patient, organized, and fair. The homeowner hears,) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 191.50 Tm
("This person is not trying to trap me. They are helping me compare.") Tj
/F2 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 159.10 Tm
