/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 133.10 Tm
(Do not attack the utility company emotionally. The point is not to create anger; it is to create) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 119.70 Tm
(awareness. Stick to the structure: current payment, lack of ownership, rate uncertainty, and) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 106.30 Tm
(comparison.) Tj
