/F2 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 444.30 Tm
(How to Frame the Application) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 418.30 Tm
(The application should not feel like a trap. It should feel like a qualification step. Explain what) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 404.90 Tm
(information is used, why it is needed, and what happens next.) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 384.50 Tm
("The application tells us what option you qualify for. Before we submit anything, I want you to know) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 371.50 Tm
(what it checks, what it does not check, and what the result means.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 351.50 Tm
