/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 338.10 Tm
(trust immediately.) Tj
/F2 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 305.70 Tm
(How to Frame Documents and Signing) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 279.70 Tm
(The signing moment is where many deals become fragile. The wrong frame is, "Tap here quickly." The) Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 266.30 Tm
(right frame is, "Review this, understand it, and ask me questions before you sign.") Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 245.90 Tm
("These documents put the program details in writing. I will show you where the key terms are:) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 232.90 Tm
(payment, system details, cancellation terms, installation process, and responsibilities. Ask me) Tj
/F3 9.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.00 219.90 Tm
(anything before you tap.") Tj
/F1 9.8 Tf
1 0 0 1 54.00 199.90 Tm
